            How to thrive in a turbulent economy.
            Proven financial strategies for today's world that will give you freedom and peace of mind.
             How to focus on what you do best and let go of the rest.
            Easy-to-implement Action Steps with every chapter.
            Plus, the latest insights from the authors to help you prosper in all areas of your life</p>
            
